  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Send 100 Somali PastoralGirls to school in Garissa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will support 100 Somali Pastoral girls access education in the secondary level in the arid region of Garissa, Northern Kenya. Pastoralist Girls Initiative will pay school fees for 100 girls for 1 year, procure books, uniform, sanitary towels and pants to ease the burden of the poverty stricken families who  due to harsh climatic condition and their nomadic lifestyle of moving  from one place to another in search of pasture and water can not afford to send their girls to school.</narrative>
  </description>
